This is a Camel components supporting the ZeroMQ library. It's also an attempt to show how to integrate Camel with any native library/transport.
For compiling this component you need to install cmake (http://www.cmake.org), swig (http://www.swig.org) and boost (www.boost.org) besides
ZeroMQ (www.zeromq.org) off course.
This version is compiled against the latest available version of zeromq2 available at: http://github.com/sustrik/zeromq2
